section.section:
Of the 13 members, 10 shall be appointed by the Governor with the advice of the Secretary as follows:
1 shall be the pesticides coordinator or the pesticides coordinator's designee for the Cooperative Extension Service of the University of Maryland;
1 shall be from the State Department of Agriculture;
1 shall be from the Department of Labor, Licensing, and Regulation, Division of Labor and Industry;
1 shall be from the Department of Natural Resources;
1 shall be the State Fire Marshal or the State Fire Marshal's designee;
1 shall be from an industry that generates hazardous substances;
1 shall be from the hazardous substance disposal and management industry;
1 shall be from an industry that generates low-level nuclear waste;
1 shall be from the low-level nuclear waste management industry; and
1 shall be an individual who is engaged in the business of resource recovery.
